exceptions.exn: In environment A : Set A0, A1 : A eqA : A -> A -> Prop plusA : A -> A -> A invA : A -> A minusA, multA : A -> A -> A divA : A -> forall b : A, ~ eqA b A0 -> A cs : CoefStructure A A0 A1 eqA plusA invA minusA multA divA eqA_dec : forall a b : A, {eqA a b} + {~ eqA a b} n : nat ltM : mon n -> mon n -> Prop ltM_dec : forall a b : mon n, {ltM a b} + {ltM b a} + {a = b} os : OrderStructure (mon n) (zero_mon n) ltM (mult_mon n) L : list (poly A0 eqA ltM) p, q : poly A0 eqA ltM H : Cb A A0 eqA plusA multA eqA_dec n ltM ltM_dec q (addEnd A A0 eqA n ltM p L) Unable to unify "Cb A A0 eqA plusA multA eqA_dec n ltM ltM_dec q (addEnd A A0 eqA n ltM p L)" with "Cb A A0 eqA plusA multA eqA_dec n ltM ltM_dec q (p :: L)".

original: intros L p q H. apply H.
